  "content": "<div class=\"css-376mun\"><span id=\"content\"><span class=\"RichText ztext CopyrightRichText-richText css-10o75c2\" options=\"[object Object]\" itemprop=\"text\"><p data-first-child=\"\" data-pid=\"GEJrbVVW\">单纯从超声检查中比较难直接发现这些异常如：下尿道口下裂、外阴畸形、睾丸下降、隐睾等。</p><p data-pid=\"IdN36-1H\">排查两性畸形，产检除了超声检查发现胎儿身体结构和性别特征外，还可以借助产前诊断的方式（<span><a class=\"RichContent-EntityWord css-b7erz1\" data-za-not-track-link=\"true\" data-paste-text=\"true\" href=\"https://zhida.zhihu.com/search?content_id=592676165&amp;content_type=Answer&amp;match_order=1&amp;q=%E7%BE%8A%E6%B0%B4%E7%A9%BF%E5%88%BA&amp;zhida_source=entity\" target=\"_blank\">羊水穿刺<svg width=\"10px\" height=\"10px\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" class=\"ZDI ZDI--FourPointedStar16 css-1dvsrp\" fill=\"currentColor\"><path d=\"m5.068 9.267-3.08-.77a.512.512 0 0 1 0-.994l3.08-.77a2.289 2.289 0 0 0 1.665-1.665l.77-3.08a.512.512 0 0 1 .994 0l.77 3.08c.205.82.845 1.46 1.665 1.665l3.08.77a.512.512 0 0 1 0 .994l-3.08.77a2.29 2.29 0 0 0-1.665 1.665l-.77 3.08a.512.512 0 0 1-.994 0l-.77-3.08a2.289 2.289 0 0 0-1.665-1.665Z\"></path></svg></a></span>）提取胎儿的细胞用于染色体或<span><a class=\"RichContent-EntityWord css-b7erz1\" data-za-not-track-link=\"true\" data-paste-text=\"true\" href=\"https://zhida.zhihu.com/search?content_id=592676165&amp;content_type=Answer&amp;match_order=1&amp;q=%E5%9F%BA%E5%9B%A0%E6%A3%80%E6%B5%8B&amp;zhida_source=entity\" target=\"_blank\">基因检测<svg width=\"10px\" height=\"10px\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" class=\"ZDI ZDI--FourPointedStar16 css-1dvsrp\" fill=\"currentColor\"><path d=\"m5.068 9.267-3.08-.77a.512.512 0 0 1 0-.994l3.08-.77a2.289 2.289 0 0 0 1.665-1.665l.77-3.08a.512.512 0 0 1 .994 0l.77 3.08c.205.82.845 1.46 1.665 1.665l3.08.77a.512.512 0 0 1 0 .994l-3.08.77a2.29 2.29 0 0 0-1.665 1.665l-.77 3.08a.512.512 0 0 1-.994 0l-.77-3.08a2.289 2.289 0 0 0-1.665-1.665Z\"></path></svg></a></span>。</p><blockquote data-pid=\"dCPUQp4S\">染色体数量异常：如，21/18/13−<span><a class=\"RichContent-EntityWord css-b7erz1\" data-za-not-track-link=\"true\" data-paste-text=\"true\" href=\"https://zhida.zhihu.com/search?content_id=592676165&amp;content_type=Answer&amp;match_order=1&amp;q=%E4%B8%89%E4%BD%93%E7%BB%BC%E5%90%88%E7%97%87&amp;zhida_source=entity\" target=\"_blank\">三体综合症<svg width=\"10px\" height=\"10px\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" class=\"ZDI ZDI--FourPointedStar16 css-1dvsrp\" fill=\"currentColor\"><path d=\"m5.068 9.267-3.08-.77a.512.512 0 0 1 0-.994l3.08-.77a2.289 2.289 0 0 0 1.665-1.665l.77-3.08a.512.512 0 0 1 .994 0l.77 3.08c.205.82.845 1.46 1.665 1.665l3.08.77a.512.512 0 0 1 0 .994l-3.08.77a2.29 2.29 0 0 0-1.665 1.665l-.77 3.08a.512.512 0 0 1-.994 0l-.77-3.08a2.289 2.289 0 0 0-1.665-1.665Z\"></path></svg></a></span>，XXX超雌，47 XXY克氏、XYY超雄，45x等等；<br>染色体片段异常：如，15q25缺失综合症【主要临床表现包括发育迟缓、身材矮小、面部畸形（包括肌病性面容，眼距过宽，睑裂下斜，上嘴唇外翻，唇裂，腭裂等），其他包括细胞性贫血、血栓形成、室间隔缺损、右位心、<span><a class=\"RichContent-EntityWord css-b7erz1\" data-za-not-track-link=\"true\" data-paste-text=\"true\" href=\"https://zhida.zhihu.com/search?content_id=592676165&amp;content_type=Answer&amp;match_order=1&amp;q=%E6%BC%8F%E6%96%97%E8%83%B8&amp;zhida_source=entity\" target=\"_blank\">漏斗胸<svg width=\"10px\" height=\"10px\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" class=\"ZDI ZDI--FourPointedStar16 css-1dvsrp\" fill=\"currentColor\"><path d=\"m5.068 9.267-3.08-.77a.512.512 0 0 1 0-.994l3.08-.77a2.289 2.289 0 0 0 1.665-1.665l.77-3.08a.512.512 0 0 1 .994 0l.77 3.08c.205.82.845 1.46 1.665 1.665l3.08.77a.512.512 0 0 1 0 .994l-3.08.77a2.29 2.29 0 0 0-1.665 1.665l-.77 3.08a.512.512 0 0 1-.994 0l-.77-3.08a2.289 2.289 0 0 0-1.665-1.665Z\"></path></svg></a></span>、膈疝、隐睾、腹股沟疝、精神运动发育延迟、多动症、<span><a class=\"RichContent-EntityWord css-b7erz1\" data-za-not-track-link=\"true\" data-paste-text=\"true\" href=\"https://zhida.zhihu.com/search?content_id=592676165&amp;content_type=Answer&amp;match_order=1&amp;q=%E6%B3%A8%E6%84%8F%E5%8A%9B%E7%BC%BA%E9%99%B7&amp;zhida_source=entity\" target=\"_blank\">注意力缺陷<svg width=\"10px\" height=\"10px\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" class=\"ZDI ZDI--FourPointedStar16 css-1dvsrp\" fill=\"currentColor\"><path d=\"m5.068 9.267-3.08-.77a.512.512 0 0 1 0-.994l3.08-.77a2.289 2.289 0 0 0 1.665-1.665l.77-3.08a.512.512 0 0 1 .994 0l.77 3.08c.205.82.845 1.46 1.665 1.665l3.08.77a.512.512 0 0 1 0 .994l-3.08.77a2.29 2.29 0 0 0-1.665 1.665l-.77 3.08a.512.512 0 0 1-.994 0l-.77-3.08a2.289 2.289 0 0 0-1.665-1.665Z\"></path></svg></a></span>和自闭症特征，患者出生时即可发病。个体间临床表现具有差异性。】</blockquote><figure data-size=\"normal\"><noscript><img src=\"https://pic1.zhimg.com/50/v2-f2749600fc0446be69bd6ff40f989e42_720w.jpg?source=1def8aca\" data-rawwidth=\"363\" data-rawheight=\"293\" data-size=\"normal\" data-original-token=\"v2-972267ba0b92f1897ac9015920fd71ca\" data-default-watermark-src=\"https://pic1.zhimg.com/50/v2-86c9db716426e70ec13825ceeb82c769_720w.jpg?source=1def8aca\" class=\"content_image\" width=\"363\"/></noscript><div><img src=\"https://pic1.zhimg.com/80/v2-f2749600fc0446be69bd6ff40f989e42_720w.webp?source=1def8aca\" data-rawwidth=\"363\" data-rawheight=\"293\" data-size=\"normal\" data-original-token=\"v2-972267ba0b92f1897ac9015920fd71ca\" data-default-watermark-src=\"https://pic1.zhimg.com/50/v2-86c9db716426e70ec13825ceeb82c769_720w.jpg?source=1def8aca\" class=\"content_image lazy\" width=\"363\" data-actualsrc=\"https://pic1.zhimg.com/50/v2-f2749600fc0446be69bd6ff40f989e42_720w.jpg?source=1def8aca\" height=\"293\" data-lazy-status=\"ok\"></div><figcaption>克氏综合症</figcaption></figure><p data-pid=\"28Ecj5i9\">产检是尽量避免胎儿出生缺陷，并不只是性别的确定，在进行任何检查之前一定要找专业医生了解清楚。</p></span><span id=\"VirtualCatalogAnchorPoint\"></span></span></div>",
  "excerpt": "单纯从超声检查中比较难直接发现这些异常如：下尿道口下裂、外阴畸形、睾丸下降、隐睾等。\n\n排查两性畸形，产检除了超声检查发现胎儿身体结构和性别特征外，还可以借助产前诊断的方式（羊水穿刺）提取胎儿的细胞用于染色体或基因检测。\n\n染色体数量异常：如，21/18/13−三体综合症，XXX超雌，47 XXY克氏、XYY超雄，45x等等；\n染色体片段异常：如，15q25缺失综合症【主要临床表现包括发育迟缓、身材矮小、面部畸形（包括肌病性面容，眼距过宽，睑裂下斜，上嘴唇外翻，唇裂，腭裂等），其他包括细胞性贫血、血栓形成、室间隔缺损、右位心、漏斗胸、膈疝、隐睾、腹股沟疝、精神运动发育延迟、多动症、注意力缺陷和",
